Invocation Name: x. ninety six
des:
X96, Utah's Original Alternative
Once enabled, just say: "Alexa, open the x. ninety six" and Alexa will guide you from there!
After that, you can say things like:
 * "Listen to on demand"
 * "Resume"
 * "On demand options"
When playing audio, you can say:
 * Alexa, pause
When playing on-demand content, you can skip to an older show by saying:
 * Alexa, next
And navigate to the previous segment by saying:
 * Alexa, go back
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
